<div id="review_210705904" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/210705904" />
    <a title="Barnabas Piper" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6330303-barnabas-piper"><img alt="Barnabas Piper" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1510346774p2/6330303.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/210705904?book_show_action=true">Mar 04, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Barnabas Piper" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Barnabas Piper" href="/user/show/6330303-barnabas-piper">Barnabas Piper</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer210705904" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17633405986518878797">Well, all the recommendations I received for this over the years were correct with a bullet. What a magnificent book. Some books teach. Some books inspire. Some books reveal. This did all that, but what it really did was help me love Jesus more and know the love of Jesus more. I loved Manning&apos;s bluntness and ability to incisively get to the heart of grace and God&apos;s love. </span>
  <span id="freeText17633405986518878797" style="display:none">Well, all the recommendations I received for this over the years were correct with a bullet. What a magnificent book. Some books teach. Some books inspire. Some books reveal. This did all that, but what it really did was help me love Jesus more and know the love of Jesus more. I loved Manning's bluntness and ability to incisively get to the heart of grace and God's love. </span>
  <a data-text-id="17633405986518878797" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
